          "title": "DOCKER ROLLOUT",
          "summary": "docker rollout is a Docker CLI plugin that updates Docker Compose services. It features zero downtime deployment for Docker Compose services and it supports Docker healthchecks. docker rollout currently only supports services with scale 1 and requires a proxy to route traffic.",
