          "order": 2,
          "title": "NANGO",
          "summary": "Nango is a service that contains everything required to work with APIs that use OAuth. It contains out-of-the-box support for over 40 APIs, a frontend SDK to trigger new OAuth flows, and a backend SDK & REST API to retrieve fresh access tokens for API calls. Nango can be deployed in 15 minutes.",
